This paper discusses various techniques for information hiding, including steganography and digital watermarking. These techniques are commonly used in the fields of computer security (cs.CR), multimedia (cs.MM), information retrieval (cs.IR), computer vision (cs.CV), and data structures (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
